title: Apple updates iMac family with new Retina displays, unveils all-new Magic Keyboard, Magic Mouse 2 and Magic Trackpad 2
text:
Apple updates iMac family with new Retina displays, unveils all-new Magic Keyboard, Magic Mouse 2 and Magic Trackpad 2 
Published By: MacDailyNews.com - Today 
Apple today updated the entire iMac family, bringing a stunning new Retina 4K display to the 21.5-inch iMac
